'''氪-85''' ('''氪<sup>85</sup>''')是[[氪|氪]]的一种[[放射性同位素|放射性同位素]]。它的[[半衰期|半衰期]]为10.756年，最大[[放射性|衰变能]]为687[[千电子伏特|千电子伏特]](keV)<ref name=TOI>{{cite web |title= WWW Table of Radioactive Isotopes - Kr85 |url= http://ie.lbl.gov/toi/nuclide.asp?iZA=360085 |publisher= Lawrence Berkeley Laboratories, USA |access-date= 2015-05-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150611153047/http://ie.lbl.gov/toi/nuclide.asp?iZA=360085 |archive-date= 2015-06-11 |url-status= dead }}</ref>，它衰变为稳定的[[铷|铷]]-85。最常见的衰变(99.57%)是通过[[β粒子|β粒子]]辐射，最大能量为687[[电子伏特|电子伏特]]，平均能量为251电子伏特。第二种最常见的β粒子辐射为0.43%的衰变，最大能量173千电子伏，其次是[[伽马射线|伽马射线]]辐射(能量为514千电子伏)<ref>{{cite web |author= M. Gorden |title= Pinellas Plant – Occupational Environmental Dose rev1 |url= https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ocas/pdfs/tbd/pine4-r1.pdf |publisher= ORAU |date= 15 July 2011 |access-date= 2015-05-30 |display-authors= etal |archive-date= 2021-03-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210326131857/https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ocas/pdfs/tbd/pine4-r1.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref> 其他衰变模式则概率很小且辐射的伽马射线能量也较低<ref name=TOI/><ref>{{cite journal |author= H. Sievers |title= Nuclear data sheets update for A=85 |journal= Nuclear Data Sheets |volume= 62 |pages= 271–325 |year=1991 |doi=10.1016/0090-3752(91)80016-Y|bibcode=1991NDS....62..271S }}</ref>。 

就[[游离辐射#危害性与辐射的作用方式|辐射危害性]]而言，在不考虑[[衰变链#种类|氡衰变链]]其余部分的前提下，440[[贝克勒尔|贝克]]氪<sup>85</sup>相当于1贝克的[[氡-222|氡-222]]。

==大气层中的分布==
{{Medium-lived fission products}}
===自然发生===
氪-85是由[[宇宙线|宇宙射线]]与大气层中稳定的[[氪的同位素|氪-84]]相互作用产生的少量物质，自然来源在大气层中保持着约0.09[[贝克勒尔|拍贝克]]的均衡量<ref name=global2005>{{cite journal |author= K. Winger |title= A new compilation of the atmospheric 85krypton inventories from 1945 to 2000 and its evaluation in a global transport model |journal= JRNL of Envir Radioactivity |volume= 80 |issue= 2 |pages= 183–215 |year=2005 |doi=10.1016/j.jenvrad.2004.09.005 |pmid= 15701383 |display-authors=etal}}</ref>。

===人工生产===
然而，截至2009年，由于人为因素，大气层中的总量估计已达到5500拍贝克<ref name=global2013>{{cite journal |author= J. Ahlswede|title= Update and improvement of the global krypton-85 emission inventory|journal= JRNL of Envir Radioactivity|volume= 115|pages= 34–42|year= 2013|doi= 10.1016/j.jenvrad.2012.07.006|pmid= 22858641|display-authors=etal}}</ref>。2000年底，估计为4800拍贝克，1973年估计为1961拍贝克(53兆[[居里_(单位)|居里]])<ref name=r0>{{cite journal |title= Atmospheric Concentrations and Inventory of Krypton-85 in 1973|last= Telegadas|first= K.|date= 1975-11-28|journal= Science|doi= 10.1126/science.190.4217.882|last2= Ferber|first2= G. J.|publisher= American Association for the Advancement of Science|jstor=1741777|volume=190|issue= 4217|pages=882–883|bibcode= 1975Sci...190..882T}}</ref>。这些人为来源中最重要的是[[核燃料再处理|核燃料再处理]]<ref name=global2005/><ref name=global2013/><ref name=r0/>，核裂变每1000次产生约3个氪-85原子，即裂变产出率为0.3%<ref>{{cite book |url= https://www-nds.iaea.org/sgnucdat/c3.htm |access-date= 2015-06-01 |title= Cumulative Fission Yields |date= August 2005 |work= JEFF-3.1 Nuclear Data Library, JEFF Report 21, OECD/NEA, Paris, France, 2006 |isbn= 978-92-64-02314-7 |archive-date= 2021-03-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210308040829/https://www-nds.iaea.org/sgnucdat/c3.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。大部分或全部氪-85被保留在[[乏核燃料|乏核燃料]]棒中；从反应堆排出的乏燃料含有0.13-1.8拍贝克/毫克的氪-85<ref name=global2005/>，其中一些乏燃料会被[[核燃料再处理|再处理]]。当乏燃料溶解处理时，则会释放气态氪<sup>85</sup>到大气中。原则上，可将这种氪气作为[[放射性废料|核废料]]收集和储存起来，或加以利用。截至2000年，估计全球从再处理活动中释放的氪-85累积量为1060拍贝克<ref name=global2005/>。由于放射性衰变，上述存在于全球大气层中的氪-85量小于这一数值；只有一小部分溶解在深海中<ref name=global2005/>。

其他人造资源对总量作用不大，大气层[[核试验|核试验]]释放了约111-185拍贝克<ref name=global2005/>；1979年[[三哩岛核泄漏事故|三里岛核电站]]事故释放了约1.6拍贝克(43千居里)<ref>{{cite web |title= U.S. NRC: Backgrounder on the Three Mile Island accident |url= https://www.nrc.gov/reading-rm/doc-collections/fact-sheets/3mile-isle.html |publisher= U.S. Nuclear Regulatory Commission |access-date= 2015-05-31 |date= 2014-12-12 |archive-date= 2021-11-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211115101945/https://www.nrc.gov/reading-rm/doc-collections/fact-sheets/3mile-isle.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>；[[切尔诺贝利核事故|切尔诺贝利核事故]]释放了大约35拍贝克<ref name=global2005/><ref name=global2013/>；而[[福岛第一核电站事故|福岛第一核电站事故]]则估计释放了44-84拍贝克<ref name=Lin2015>{{cite journal |author= W. Lin |title= Radioactivity impacts of the Fukushima Nuclear Accident on the atmosphere |journal= Atmospheric Environment |volume= 102 |pages=311–322 |year=2015 |doi=10.1016/j.atmosenv.2014.11.047|display-authors=etal|bibcode=2015AtmEn.102..311L }}</ref>。

1976年，大气层中氪-85的平均浓度约为0.6[[贝克勒尔|吉贝克]]/米<sup>3</sup>，到2005年已增至约1.3吉贝克/米<sup>3</sup><ref name=global2005/><ref name=Ross2010>{{cite techreport |author= O. Ross |title= Simulations of the atmospheric krypton-85 to assess the detectability of clandestine nuclear reprocessing |work= Symposium on International Safeguards: Preparing for Future Verification Challenges; Vienna (Austria); 1-5 Nov 2010 |publisher=IAEA-CN-184 |url=http://www.iaea.org/OurWork/SV/Safeguards/Symposium/2010/Documents/PapersRepository/034.pdf|display-authors=etal}}</ref>，这只是近似的全球平均值；核废料处理设施周围的局部浓度较高，且北半球的浓度通常高于南半球。

对于广域大气层监测来说，氪-85是反映秘密分离钚的最佳指标<ref>{{Citation|doi=10.1016/j.jenvrad.2003.09.002|title=Conclusions on plutonium separation from atmospheric krypton-85 measured at various distances from the Karlsruhe reprocessing plant|year=2004|last1=Kalinowski|first1=Martin B.|last2=Sartorius|first2=Hartmut|last3=Uhl|first3=Stefan|last4=Weiss|first4=Wolfgang|journal=Journal of Environmental Radioactivity|volume=73|issue=2|pages=203–22|pmid=15023448}}</ref>。

氪-85的释放增加了大气层的导电性，靠近排放源的地方，气象影响预计会更强<ref>{{cite journal |last= Harrison|first= R. G.|last2= ApSimon|first2= H. M.|date= 1994-02-01|title= Krypton-85 pollution and atmospheric electricity|url= https://archive.org/details/sim_atmospheric-environment_1994-02_28_4/page/637|journal= Atmospheric Environment|volume= 28|issue= 4|pages= 637–648|doi= 10.1016/1352-2310(94)90041-8|bibcode= 1994AtmEn..28..637H}}</ref>。

==工业用途==
氪-85被用于娱乐业中常用的电弧放电灯，如大型镝灯及[[高强度气体放电灯|高强度气体放电灯]]<ref>[http://www.spectragases.com/AssetMgmt/getDocument.aspx?assetid=618 Krypton-85 (PDF)]. Spectragases.com (2004-12-30). Retrieved on 2013-07-25.</ref><ref name=LampType>{{Citation|url=http://www.elcfed.org/2_lighting_types.html |title=Lamp Types |publisher=European Lamp Companies Federation |access-date=2012-11-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ByFh9L4o?url=http://www.elcfed.org/2_lighting_types.html |archive-date=2012-11-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=Ion>{{Citation|year=2009 |title=Ionizing Substances in Lighting Products |publisher=European Lamp Companies Federation |url=http://www.elcfed.org/documents/Ionizing_Substances_Lighting_products_2003_rev_2009_final.pdf |access-date=2012-11-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ByG02MTB?url=http://www.elcfed.org/documents/Ionizing_Substances_Lighting_products_2003_rev_2009_final.pdf |archive-date=2012-11-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=Transport>{{Citation|author=NRPB and GRS |year=2001 |title=Transport of Consumer Goods containing Small Quantities of Radioactive Materials |publisher=European Commission |url=http://ec.europa.eu/energy/nuclear/transport/doc/final-version-study1.pdf |access-date=2012-11-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ByH7p9nP?url=http://ec.europa.eu/energy/nuclear/transport/doc/final-version-study1.pdf |archive-date=2012-11-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=HPA>{{Citation|year=2011 |title=Assessment of the Radiological Impact of the Transport and Disposal of Light Bulbs Containing Tritium, Krypton-85 and Radioisotopes of Thorium |publisher=Health Protection Agency |url=http://www.hpa.org.uk/web/HPAwebFile/HPAweb_C/1287143225736 |access-date=2012-11-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ByJGrM6R?url=http://www.hpa.org.uk/webc/HPAwebFile/HPAweb_C/1287143225736 |archive-date=2012-11-06 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。氙灯放电管中充入氪-85使氙灯更易被点燃<ref name=LampType/>，早期实验性氪-85照明的开发包括1957年设计的铁路信号灯<ref>{{cite news|url= https://www.newspapers.com/clip/2521970/krypton85_powered_railroad_signal/|title= Make A-powered Rail Signal Light in D&RGW Labs|date= 1957-02-17|access-date= 2015-05-31|via= Newspapers.com|newspaper= The Ogden Standard-Examiner|archive-date= 2016-08-19|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160819001029/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/2521970/krypton85_powered_railroad_signal/|dead-url= no}}</ref>和1969年在[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]竖立的公路照明标志<ref>{{cite news|url= https://www.newspapers.com/clip/2521877/krypton85_nuclear_powered_highway_sign/|title= Atomic sign glows day and night here|last= Davis|first= Al|date= 1970-01-04|access-date= 2015-05-31|via= Newspapers.com|newspaper= Arizona Republic|archive-date= 2016-08-19|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160819041650/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/2521877/krypton85_nuclear_powered_highway_sign/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。目前[[随机数生成|随机数服务器]]HotBits使用了氪-85封闭容器(暗指[[放射性同位素|放射性同位素]]是[[量子力学|量子力学]]的无序状态之源)<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.wired.com/wired/archive/11.08/random.html | work = Wired Magazine | title = Totally Random | volume = 11 | issue = 8 | date = August 2003 | accessdate = 2021-02-15 | archive-date = 2014-03-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324174805/http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/11.08/random.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

氪-85还用于检查飞机部件的小缺陷，氪-85能穿透小裂纹，通过放射自显影方式检测损伤的存在，这种方法被称为“氪气体渗透成像”。气体渗透的裂口比“着色浸透探伤检测”和“荧光渗透检测”中使用的液体要更小<ref>Glatz, Joseph. [https://web.archive.org/web/20080720084341/http://www.asnt.org/publications/materialseval/solution/decsolutions/decsolutions.htm Krypton Gas Penetrant Imaging – A Valuable Tool for Ensuring Structural Integrity in Aircraft Engine Components]. American Society for Nondestructive Testing</ref>。

氪-85还应用于冷阴极稳压电子管，如5651型<ref>[http://www.oddmix.com/tubes/5651.html 5651 Sylvania Voltage Regulator Stabilizer Electron Tube] {{Wayback|url=http://www.oddmix.com/tubes/5651.html |date=20160304220721 }}. Oddmix.com (2013-05-15). Retrieved on 2013-07-25.</ref>。

